title: Disgraced FBI Agent: Jan. 6 Worse Than 9/11
itunes:title: Disgraced FBI Agent: Jan. 6 Worse Than 9/11
description: Yesterday appearing on MSNBC, disgraced former FBI Agent Peter Strzok claimed that "when you look at something that's an attack on democracy... 9/11 is nothing compared to January 6th." Jordan, Logan, and the Sekulow team break down Strzok's comments and what it could tell us about how the Deep State intelligence community views their role in politics. This and more today on Sekulow.
